Package com.bakdata.dedupe.fusion

Class FusedValue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bakdata.dedupe.fusion.FusedValue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the record
    public final class FusedValue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A fused value with contextual information. If any exception occurred during fusion (exceptions is not empty), the value should be considered incomplete.

    A fusion may fail if there is no obvious representation of a certain piece of information or ultimately requried fields are unset.

    A IncompleteFusionHandler may try to find a better solution (possibly with human interaction).
